{
  "stem": "7455.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would not say that the government policy is such, but there were some rude people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were primitive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they went to a movie, like military movie, where they have military go-- propaganda, there were only several men's rooms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they will go out to a side street and, in broad light, relieve themself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The next day, from the sanitation, had to clean up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The women were dressed shabbily because they were poor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The bought out everything they could see and shipped to Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They did not give-- bring-- import anything-- only watermelons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when I think of the Nazis and the Germans, that complaint is very minimal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- but I'm just relating our impression at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In 1941, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the, the G-- the Germans violated their pact with Russia and attacked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was confusion in our town, because the first thing, the Russians had to flee with their families.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were packing up and running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Naturally, the Communists were the first one to run, because if the Germans come, they would be the first ones to be shot.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some single people who, who ran with Russia-- not that they were Communists.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, why didn't we run with the Russians?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't like them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had our home, and we could not-- we did not anticipate what's going to-- that such tragedy's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, because our highway not far from us, the main road, was filled with tanks, the Russians, they were posing resistance but retreating to fortify themselves on their territory using our territory as a buffer.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And bombs were flying-- falling, and artillery, and anti-craft artillery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were, again, in the cellar with our tenants, neighbors, and for several days.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
